ANVI REST API documentation

This is a REST API documentation for data platform and its modules , which is based on OpenAPI (Swagger) Specification. You can generate your client here.
More information: https://helloreverb.com
Contact Info: hello@helloreverb.com
Version: 1.8.1
BasePath:/api/v1
All rights reserved
http://apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html

Access

  1. APIKey KeyParamName:Authorization-Token KeyInQuery:false KeyInHeader:true
  2. HTTP Basic Authentication

Returns a collection of Library records

Request headers

Query parameters

select (optional)
Query Parameter — Fields according to Library metadata. For example: id, name, createdAt, ...
where (optional)
Query Parameter — There are a lot of filter types supported. You can learn all of them if you trace what's requested by Atro UI in the network tab in your browser console (press F12 key to open the console).
offset (optional)
Query Parameter —
maxSize (optional)
Query Parameter —
sortBy (optional)
Query Parameter —
asc (optional)
Query Parameter —
